\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
g(x)=\sum_{y\in b^{-1}(x)}\;\frac{f(y)}{b^{\prime}(y)}\label{eq:}\end{equation}

\end_inset 

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $b^{\prime}(y)$
\end_inset 

 is the derivative of 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset 

